      "id": "PopularPost119108",
      "post_content": "There are so many great things about this card... it's efficient. It's a classic fantasy monster/creature. It's first strike in monoblack, something that still, to this day, only appears on 20-odd creatures. It has fantastic symmetry with [White Knight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=1370). It has very cool flavour text.\n  \n   \n4.5/5\n  ",
