      "id": "PopularPost45644",
      "post_content": "At a time when vanilla 2/2's cost 3 mana, Black Knight epitomized efficiency. Not only did he have a converted mana cost of 2, but he had first strike and protection from white. Black Knight was soon joined by [Order of the Ebon Hand](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of the Ebon Hand) as black's premier answers to the white weenie hoards that dominated the tournament scenes and casual play during the latter half of 1994 into 1995.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost45644\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">At a time when vanilla 2/2's cost 3 mana, Black Knight epitomized efficiency.  Not only did he have a converted mana cost of 2, but he had first strike and protection from white.  Black Knight was soon joined by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Order of the Ebon Hand\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of the Ebon Hand\">Order of the Ebon Hand</a> as black's premier answers to the white weenie hoards that dominated the tournament scenes and casual play during the latter half of 1994 into 1995.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '45644'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (1/12/2010 9:42:32 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Right